sequenceDiagram
    participant Test as Test Script
    participant API as Studio API
    participant Browser as Playwright Browser
    participant Canvas as Studio Canvas

    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
    Note over Test,Canvas: STEP 1 -- Apply the token
    Test->>API: Apply token to the widget
    API-->>Test: Done - Token applied
    end

    rect rgb(227, 242, 253)
    Note over Test,Canvas: STEP 2 -- Find the widget on canvas
    Test->>Browser: Open the canvas page
    Browser->>Canvas: Load the widget
    Test->>Browser: Find widget element using XPath
    Browser->>Canvas: Locate the element
    end

    rect rgb(243, 229, 245)
    Note over Test,Canvas: STEP 3 -- Read CSS and compare
    Test->>Browser: Read CSS value (getComputedStyle)
    Browser-->>Test: Return value e.g. rgb(98, 0, 238)
    Test->>Test: Convert to hex e.g. #6200EE
    Test->>Test: Compare with expected token value
    end
